---
title: Zesty Cod en Papillote with Toasted Moroccan Couscous
description: Unwrapping this package of delicious cod and fragrant orange couscous topped with almonds will make your kitchen smell as good as you’ll feel after digging in. We’re betting this will become your new favourite way to cook fish.
